- Mobile app integration

## Troubleshooting

**Camera not working:**
- Check if your webcam is connected
- Ensure no other application is using the camera
- Try changing `cv2.VideoCapture(0)` to `cv2.VideoCapture(1)`

**Model not recognizing faces:**
- Ensure you've trained the model (option 2)
- Register more students for better accuracy
- Improve lighting conditions
- Capture training photos with varied expressions

**Installation issues:**
- Make sure you have Python 3.7+
- Install Visual C++ redistributables (Windows users)
- Use a virtual environment to avoid conflicts

